Analysis of Corpus
Running corpusAnalysis.py will provide more stats into the corpus like doccument length distribution, cosine similarity bewtween documents and most frequent terms in the corpus.
booleanIndexTable.py will create a inverted index of the corpus and also return the total vocabulary size of the document after applying stopword removal and lemmatization.
